Privacy Policy of Swimming Pool Calculator app 

The application has not been programmed to collect any personally identifiable information. Any data created inside the application (like application preferences)  
is stored locally in your device only, and can be simply erased by clearing the app's data or uninstalling it. No analytics software is present in the app either.


The app uses the following permissions: 

1) <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE" />
This permission is used to allow the application to store the application preferences (settings and last input data) on your device 

2) <uses-permission android:name="com.android.vending.CHECK_LICENSE"/>
This permission is used to check the license of the app - whether it was legally downloaded from Google Play store
